data.description: Welcome home! Come visit this totally remodeled four bedroom, two and a half bathroom colonial. From top to bottom this house has been renovated. Curb appeal await you here as you approach this home. Upon entering you will love the gleaming laminate flooring throughout. Entire home freshly painted. Brand new kitchen with stainless steel appliances, new cabinets and quartz countertops. Powder room on main level is totally renovated. Major systems replaced: a/c , and heating . As you proceed to the upper level, you have four bedrooms and two totally renovated bathrooms.  Ideal location close to major roads, shopping, malls and much more. Easy to show and we can accommodate a quick closing.
